{
    "title": "Petrolina Juazeiro",
    "artist": "Alceu Valença",
    "composer": "Geraldo Azevedo / Jorge De Altinho / Moraes Moreira / Francisco Agra",
    "lyricsHtml": "\n[Intro] <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>\n        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am/G\">Am/G</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7(5-)\">F#m7(5-)</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7/G#\">E7/G#</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Primeira Parte]</span>\n                \n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>                       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>       \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">   Na margem do São Francisco</span>\n            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Nasceu a beleza</span>\n         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E a natureza ela conservou</span>\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Jesus abençoou com sua mão divina</span>\n                      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Pra não morrer de saudade, vou voltar</span>\n          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Pra Petrolina</span>\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Jesus abençoou com sua mão divina</span>\n                      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Pra não morrer de saudade, vou voltar</span>\n          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Pra Petrolina</span>\n\n                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Do outro lado do rio tem uma cidade</span>\n                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Que em minha mocidade eu visitava todo dia</span>\n\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Atravessava a ponte ai que alegria</span>\n               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Chegava em Juazeiro, Juazeiro da Bahia</span>\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Atravessava a ponte ai que alegria</span>\n               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Chegava em Juazeiro, Juazeiro da Bahia</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Segunda Parte]</span>\n\n            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Hoje eu me lembro que nos tempos de</span>\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Criança</span>\n                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Esquisito era a carranca e o apito do trem</span>\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>                        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Mas achava lindo quando a ponte levantava</span>\n              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>                     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E o vapor passava num gostoso vai e vem</span>\n      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Petrolina, Juazeiro, Juazeiro, Petrolina</span>\n       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Todas duas eu acho uma coisa linda</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Eu gosto de Juazeiro e adoro Petrolina</span>\n\n                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Eu gosto de Juazeiro e adoro Petrolina</span>\n                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Eu gosto de Juazeiro e adoro Petrolina</span>\n                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Eu gosto de Juazeiro e adoro Petrolina</span>\n                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Eu gosto de Juazeiro e adoro Petrolina</span>\n\n( <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span> )\n( <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span> )\n( <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am/G\">Am/G</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m7(5-)\">F#m7(5-)</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7/G#\">E7/G#</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span> )\n                \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Primeira Parte]</span>\n                \n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>                       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>       \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">   Na margem do São Francisco</span>\n            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Nasceu a beleza</span>\n         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E a natureza ela conservou</span>\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord